### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/

### Create an order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Ravi Kumar",
  "phone_number": "+91 9876543210",
  "garments": [
    { "type": "shirt", "quantity": 3 },
    { "type": "pants", "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### Update order status (replace ORDER_ID)
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders/ORDER_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PROCESSING"
}

### Get all orders
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders

### Get filtered orders by status
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders?status=READY

### Get filtered orders by customer name
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders?customer_name=ravi

### Get filtered orders by phone number
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders?phone_number=9876

### Get filtered orders by garment type
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders?garment_type=shirt

### Get paginated orders
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders?skip=0&limit=2

### Get one order by id (replace ORDER_ID)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders/ORDER_ID

### Delete one order by id (replace ORDER_ID)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders/ORDER_ID

### Get order status history by id (replace ORDER_ID)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders/ORDER_ID/history

### Dashboard
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/dashboard

### Delayed orders report
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/reports/delayed

### Garment analytics report
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/reports/garments
